headline: GTA Online Update
subtitle: Introducing the Buckingham Miljet
content:
With a defense budget of nearly a trillion, you can bet not all US military personnel are travelling in cargo planes. This is a military-liveried business jet for the champagne jingoist.

This is a giant, 16-seater military-grade Jetliner for soaring through the skies of Los Santos and Blaine County and can be test piloted in the following Races:
- ‘‘Flying Colors’‘
- ‘‘Humane Race’‘

Available to purchase now from Elitastravel.com.
